<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1">
	<title></title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/swiper.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="swiper-nav swiper-container" style="margin-top:10px;">
		<div class="swiper-wrapper">
			<div class="swiper-slide"><span>一、绑定微信</span></div>
			<div class="swiper-slide"><span>二、微信权限设置</span></div>
			<div class="swiper-slide"><span>三、关注生鲜港微信公众号</span></div>
			<div class="swiper-slide"><span>四、微信账号注册</span></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="swiper-pages swiper-container">
		<div class="swiper-wrapper">
			<div class="swiper-slide">
				<div class="swiper-container scroll-container">
					<div class="swiper-scrollbar"></div>
					<div class="swiper-wrapper">
						<div class="swiper-slide">
							<div class="page-inner">
													<p class="text"> 点击 【运营中心—微信推送—微信信息接收人】，
点击【新增】按钮，在新增行输入信息，然后点击【保存】按钮</p>
					<p class="img" ><img src="step1.png" /></p>
								
								
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="swiper-slide">
				<div class="swiper-container scroll-container">
					<div class="swiper-scrollbar"></div>
					<div class="swiper-wrapper">
						<div class="swiper-slide">
							<div class="page-inner">
	<p class="text"> 点击 【运营中心—微信推送—人员微信消息配置】，在左侧选择接收人，右侧在相应权限处勾选，点击【保存】按钮。</p>
					<div class="img" ><img src="step2.png" /></div>
				
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="swiper-slide">
				<div class="swiper-container scroll-container">
					<div class="swiper-scrollbar"></div>
					<div class="swiper-wrapper">
						<div class="swiper-slide">	<div class="page-inner">
						<div class="text"> 点击【添加】，然后再点击 【公众号】，在新打开的页面里面输入 “生鲜港”，进行搜索，
						找到后，点击 【关注】 即可</p>
					<p class="img" ><img src="step3.png" /></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="swiper-slide">
				<div class="swiper-container scroll-container">
					<div class="swiper-scrollbar"></div>
					<div class="swiper-wrapper">
						<div class="swiper-slide">
							<div class="page-inner">
											<div class="text"> 点击“登陆生鲜港”，在手机注册界面一次填写姓名、手机号（必须与网页生鲜港系统注册的微信账号一致）、微信号，密码自行设置。点击“确认注册”。</p>
					<p class="img" ><img src="step4.png" /></div>
								
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>

	<script src="js/idangerous.swiper-2.0.min.js"></script>
	<script src="js/simple-app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>